<p source="SHANGBO.MINZHIFUMU 2.4.1 (STRIP 1) JI XUSHENG 2: 2"><pb xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-1a" ed="tls" n="001-1a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-1a.1">〔子〕夏問於孔子:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-1a.2">「《詩》曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-1a.3">『凱粸君子,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-1a.4">民之父母』,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-1a.5">敢問何如</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-1a.6">而可謂民之父母?」</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.MINZHIFUMU 2.4.2 (STRIPS 1-3) JI XUSHENG 2: 2"><pb xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-2a" ed="tls" n="001-2a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-2a.1">孔子答曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-2a.2">「民[之]父母乎,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-2a.3">必達於禮樂之源,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-2a.4">以致『五至』</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-2a.5">以行『三無』,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-2a.6">以橫于天下.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-2a.7">四方有敗,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-2a.8">必先知之,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-2a.9">其[可]謂民之父母矣.」</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.MINZHIFUMU 2.4.3 (STRIPS 3-5) JI XUSHENG 2: 2"><pb xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-3a" ed="tls" n="001-3a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-3a.1">子夏曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-3a.2">「敢問</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-3a.3">何謂『五至』?」</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-3a.4">孔子曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-3a.5">「『五至』乎,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-3a.6">物之所至者,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-3a.7">志亦至焉;</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-3a.8">志之[所]至者,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-3a.9">禮亦至焉;</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-3a.10">禮之所至者,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-3a.11">樂亦至焉;</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-3a.12">樂之所至者,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-3a.13">哀亦至焉,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-3a.14">哀樂相生.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-3a.15">君子以正,</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.MINZHIFUMU 2.4.4 (STRIPS 5-6) JI XUSHENG 2: 2"><pb xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-4a" ed="tls" n="001-4a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-4a.1">子夏曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-4a.2">「『五至』既聞之矣,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-4a.3">敢問何謂『三無』?」</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-4a.4">孔子曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-4a.5">「『三無』乎,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-4a.6">無聲之樂,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-4a.7">無體[之]禮,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-4a.8">無服之喪.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-4a.9">君子以此皇于天下,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-4a.10">傾耳而聽之,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-4a.11">不可得而聞也;</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-4a.12">明目而見之,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-4a.13">不可得而見也,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-4a.14">而得氣塞於四海矣,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-4a.15">此之謂『三無』.」</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.MINZHIFUMU 2.4.5 (STRIPS 6-8) JI XUSHENG 2: 2"><pb xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-5a" ed="tls" n="001-5a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-5a.1">子夏曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-5a.2">「無聲之樂,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-5a.3">無體之禮,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-5a.4">無服之喪,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-5a.5">何志是邇?」</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.MINZHIFUMU 2.4.6 (STRIPS 8-9) JI XUSHENG 2: 2"><pb xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-6a" ed="tls" n="001-6a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-6a.1">孔子曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-6a.2">「善哉! 商也,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-6a.3">將可學詩矣,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-6a.4">『成王不敢康,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-6a.5">夙夜其命又密』,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-6a.6">無聲之樂;</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-6a.7">『威儀遲遲,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-6a.8">〔不可選也]』,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-6a.9">無體之禮也.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-6a.10">『凡民有喪,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-6a.11">匍匐救之』,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-6a.12">無服〕之喪也.」</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.MINZHIFUMU 2.4.7 (STRIPS 9-10) JI XUSHENG 2: 2"><pb xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-7a" ed="tls" n="001-7a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-7a.1">子夏曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-7a.2">「其在語也,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-7a.3">美矣!</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-7a.4">宏矣!</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-7a.5">大矣!</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-7a.6">盡於[此而已乎?」</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-7a.7">孔子曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-7a.8">「何為其然!</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-7a.9">猶有五起焉.」</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-7a.10">子夏曰]:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-7a.11">[...] 可得而聞歟?」</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-7a.12">[...] "[</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.MINZHIFUMU 2.4.8 (STRIPS 11-12) JI XUSHENG 2:2-3"><pb xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-8a" ed="tls" n="001-8a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-8a.1">孔子曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-8a.2">「無聲之樂,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-8a.3">氣志不違;</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-8a.4">〔無〕體之禮,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-8a.5">威儀逮逮;</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-8a.6">無服之喪,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-8a.7">內恕巽悲.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-8a.8">無聲之樂,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-8a.9">塞于四方;</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-8a.10">無體之禮,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-8a.11">日逑月相;</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-8a.12">無服之 (12) 〔喪〕,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-8a.13">純德[同明.</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.MINZHIFUMU 2.4.9 (STRIPS 12-13) JI XUSHENG 2:3"><pb xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-9a" ed="tls" n="001-9a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-9a.1">無聲之樂,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-9a.2">施及孫子;</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-9a.3">無體之禮,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-9a.4">塞于四海;</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-9a.5">無服之喪,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-9a.6">為民父母;</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-9a.7">無聲之樂,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-9a.8">氣〔志〕既得;</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-9a.9">無體之禮,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-9a.10">威儀翼翼;</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-9a.11">無服〔之〕喪,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-9a.12">施及四國.</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.MINZHIFUMU 2.4.10 (STRIPS 13-14) JI XUSHENG 2:3"><pb xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-10a" ed="tls" n="001-10a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-10a.1">無聲之樂,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-10a.2">氣志既從;</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-10a.3">無體之禮,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-10a.4">上下和同;</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-10a.5">無服 〔之〕喪,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0035_tls_001-10a.6">以畜萬邦.」</seg></p>

